-- Lane, Scherr, Varadhan Named to Goldman’s Management Committee, Memo Shows
-- B y   C h r i s t i n e   H a r p e r
-- 2012-01-11T21:03:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-11/lane-scherr-varadhan-named-to-goldman-s-management-committee-memo-shows.html
Goldman Sachs Group Inc. (GS)  appointed
Eric S. Lane, Stephen M. Scherr and Ashok Varadhan to the New
York-based firm’s management committee, according to an internal
memo obtained by Bloomberg News.  Michael DuVally , a spokesman for the company, confirmed the
memo’s contents.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Christine Harper in New York at 
 charper@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Scheer at 
 dscheer@bloomberg.net  